page.title: 20CREDITS
page.content:
The Geography Club at Alleyne's School Stone,in association with{ Fulford Primary First School} worked on the Domesday Project May-July l985. Fulford School contributors:- pupils:-Helen Dalley,Adrian Brown,Lisa Croft,Stephen Oxby,Martin Shaw,Kym Roberts,Louise C.Also Headteacher Mrs Blood. {Alleyne's School Geography Club} pupils(age15):- Jonathan Buckley,Neil Gartland,Mark Lanyon,Scott Reay. Stuart Reid(who signed copywright form) and teachers:-Mrs Bickley,Mr Grundy, Mr Jones(who took photos and signed copywright form)
Alleyne's School minibus was used in collecting field data and the computer department helped in disc entry.
